         <div xml:lang="grc" type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><div n="r" type="textpart"><ab>

    <lb n="1"/>Ἡρακλῆ<unclear>ς</unclear> <supplied reason="lost">Κέρδω</supplied>νι ἀδελφῷ <choice><reg>πλεῖστα</reg><orig>πλῖσ<unclear>τα</unclear></orig></choice> <choice><reg>χαίρειν</reg><orig>χ<unclear>έρε</unclear>ιν</orig></choice>. πρὸ μ<unclear>ὲν</unclear> 

    <lb n="2"/><choice><reg>πάν<supplied reason="omitted">των</supplied></reg><orig>παν</orig></choice> εὔ<supplied reason="lost">χομα</supplied><unclear>ί</unclear> σε <subst><add place="inline">ὁ<unclear>λ</unclear>όκληρον</add><del rend="corrected">ο<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>οκληρον</del></subst> ἀπολαβεῖν ἅμα 

    <lb n="3"/>τῇ <choice><reg>γλ<unclear>υ</unclear>κ<unclear>υ</unclear>τά<supplied reason="omitted">τῃ</supplied></reg><orig>γλ<unclear>υ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">κ</supplied><unclear>υ</unclear>τα</orig></choice> <choice><reg>Ταφύγχει</reg><orig>Ταφύγχι</orig></choice> <choice><reg>θυγατρί</reg><orig>θυγατρος</orig></choice> σου. θαυμά

    <lb n="4" break="no"/>ζω πῶς οὐδεμίαν ἐπιστολήν <unclear>μο</unclear>ι ἔγραψας. ἐγὼ 

    <lb n="5"/>δὲ πολλάκις σοι ἔγραψα ἐπιζητῶ<unclear>ν</unclear> σου τῆς 

    <lb n="6"/>φιλίας, σὺ δὲ <unclear>μ</unclear>ίαν <num value="1"/> μοι μόνον ἔγραψας, οὐ

    <lb n="7" break="no"/>δὲ πάλιν ἐμοὶ ἔγραψας, <subst><add place="inline">ἀ<unclear>λλ</unclear>ὰ</add><del rend="corrected">α<gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"/>α</del></subst> τῷ πατρί μου ἔ<unclear>γρα</unclear>

    <lb n="8" break="no"/>ψας, οὐκ <choice><reg>ὀλίγως</reg><orig>ὀλιλίγως</orig></choice> <subst><add place="inline"><choice><reg>ἀπειλ<unclear>ῶ</unclear>ν</reg><orig>ἀπιλ<unclear>ῶ</unclear>ν</orig></choice></add><del rend="corrected">απιλ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ν</del></subst> μοι. θεὸς δὲ μό<unclear>νος</unclear> 

    <lb n="9"/>οἶδε ὅτι καθʼ ἑκάστην ἡμέραν τὸ <choice><reg>προ<supplied reason="omitted">σ</supplied>κύ

    <lb n="10" break="no"/>νημά</reg><orig>προκυ<lb n="10" break="no"/>νημά</orig></choice> σου ποιῶ, <choice><reg>εἴτε</reg><orig>ἤτε</orig></choice> παρʼ ἀνθρώποις, <choice><reg>εἴτε</reg><orig>ἤτε</orig></choice> πα<unclear>ρὰ</unclear> 

    <lb n="11"/>θεῷ. ἐπεθύμησα γάρ σε προσκυνῆσαί σε καὶ 

    <lb n="12"/>διὰ γραμμάτων ἔστʼ ἂν ὁ θεὸς <choice><reg cert="low">δώσῃ</reg><orig>δώσι</orig></choice> <expan>τὴ<ex>ν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="13"/>καλὴν ὁδ<unclear>ὸν</unclear> <unclear>κ</unclear>αὶ <unclear>πρ</unclear>οσκ<unclear>υ</unclear>νήσωμεν <choice><reg>ἀλλή

    <lb n="14" break="no"/>λους</reg><orig>ἀλλη<lb n="14" break="no"/>λοις</orig></choice>. οἶδε <unclear>γ</unclear>ὰρ ὁ Κρανᾶς ὅτι πῶς αὐτὸν ἐ

    <lb n="15" break="no"/>ξετάζω περὶ <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>μῶν καὶ <choice><reg>ἠξιούμην</reg><orig>ἠξιώμην</orig></choice> αὐ

    <lb n="16" break="no"/>τὸν ἀπὸ τῆς <choice><reg>πρώτ<unclear>η</unclear>ς</reg><orig>πρώ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>τ<unclear>η</unclear>ς</orig></choice> φορᾶς, <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να <choice><reg>ἐνέ

    <lb n="17" break="no"/>γκῃ</reg><orig>ἐνέ<lb n="17" break="no"/>κῃ</orig></choice> σοί τι καὶ οὐκ ἐδυνήθη, διότι <choice><reg>ἐκεῖ</reg><orig>ἐκῖ</orig></choice> ἦν 

    <lb n="18"/>Ἥρων ὁ δεσπότης τῶν καμήλων. καὶ 

    <lb n="19"/>νῦν αὐτὸν ἠξίωσα καὶ <choice><reg>τέτακταί</reg><orig>τέτακτέ</orig></choice> μοι. 

    <lb n="20"/>ἐὰν οὖν <choice><reg>λά<supplied reason="omitted">βω</supplied></reg><orig>λα</orig></choice>, πέμπω σοί τι. καὶ οὖν πρό

    <lb n="21" break="no"/>τρεψον αὐτὸν <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να ἀνόκνως <expan>ἡμῖ<ex>ν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="22"/>γένη<supplied reason="lost">ται</supplied> καὶ γράψον μοι τί χρῄζεις 

    <lb n="23"/>καὶ δι<supplied reason="lost">ὰ τί</supplied>νος <choice><reg>θέλεις</reg><orig>θέλις</orig></choice> πέ<add place="above">μ</add>πω. <choice><reg>οὐδεὶς</reg><orig>οὐδὶς</orig></choice> <gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="24"/>κτ<gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/>ειν παρʼ ἐμοῦ καὶ γράψον 

    <lb n="25"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="12" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <hi rend="diaeresis"><unclear>ὑ</unclear><certainty match=".." locus="value"/></hi>μῶν πάν<unclear>των</unclear> 

    <lb n="26"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="15" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>τ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <expan>ἠκούσ<unclear>αμε</unclear><ex>ν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="27"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="15" unit="character"/> θυγατρὸς περ<unclear>ὶ</unclear> 

    <lb n="28"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> ἀσπάζου Ἀμ</supplied>μώνιον τὸν ἀδε<supplied reason="lost">λ</supplied>

    <lb n="29" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">φὸν καὶ </supplied><gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><unclear>α</unclear>ν <unclear>καὶ</unclear> Ἡ<unclear>ρ</unclear>ᾶν <unclear>καὶ</unclear> 

    <lb n="30"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> καὶ τοὺς</supplied> ἡμῶν πάντα<unclear>ς</unclear> 

    <lb n="31"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="15" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>λαυρα <unclear>η</unclear>μω<gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="32"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="15" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/>. ἀσπάζου 

    <lb n="33"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="15" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>πιον καὶ ὅλους 

    <lb n="34"/><supplied reason="lost">τοὺς ἐν οἴκῳ καὶ γ</supplied><unclear>ρ</unclear>άψον περὶ τ<unclear>ῆς</unclear> 

    <lb n="35"/><supplied reason="lost">ὁλοκληρίας ὑμῶ</supplied><unclear>ν</unclear>. ἐρρῶ<unclear>σθ</unclear>αι <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>μ<unclear>ᾶς</unclear> 

    <lb n="36"/><supplied reason="lost">εὔχομαι. </supplied><supplied reason="lost" cert="low"><space extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="37,ms" rend="perpendicular"/> πέμψον ἡμῖν ὀλίγα <choice><reg>σάγγαθα</reg><orig>σάνγαθα</orig></choice> καλά, ὅσα ἐὰν εὕ<unclear>ρ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ῃς. <note xml:lang="en">vac?</note> </supplied> 
</ab></div><div n="v" type="textpart"><ab>

    <lb n="38"/><choice><reg>ἀσπάζεται</reg><orig>ἀσπάζετε</orig></choice> <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>μᾶς Κοπρῆς ὁ υ<hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>ὸς <unclear>Ἀμ</unclear>μωνοῦς ονου<gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="39"/><choice><reg>ἀσπάζεται</reg><orig>ἀσπάζετε</orig></choice> ὑμᾶς <unclear>Τ</unclear>οπαστᾶς καὶ Ἀφοῦς καὶ Ἀμμωνοῦς καὶ Ἑλένη 

    <lb n="40"/>καὶ ὁ πατὴρ καὶ ἡ μήτηρ. <choice><reg>ἀσπάζεται</reg><orig>ἀσπάζετε</orig></choice> ἡ Ἑλένη τὴν <choice><reg>θυγατέρα</reg><orig>θυγατέραν</orig></choice> σου. 

    <lb n="41"/>μὴ ἀμελήσῃς περὶ τῶν <choice><reg>σαγγάθων</reg><orig>σα<unclear>νγάθ</unclear>ων</orig></choice>. ἀσπάζου <unclear>Χ</unclear>ε<unclear>να</unclear>μοῦν τὴν 

    <lb n="42"/>γραῖαν καὶ τὰ τέκνα αὐτῆς καὶ τὸν ἀναγι<unclear>ν</unclear>ώσκοντα. 

    <lb n="43"/><choice><reg>ἐρρῶσθαι</reg><orig>ἐρρῶσθε</orig></choice> <supplied reason="lost">ὑμᾶ</supplied>ς εὐχόμεθα. 

    <lb n="44"/><expan>ἀπ<unclear>όδ</unclear><ex>ος</ex></expan> Κέρδωνι ἀδ<unclear>ε</unclear>λφῷ <g type="x"/> <expan>πα<ex>ρὰ</ex></expan> Ἡρα<unclear>κ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">λέους.</supplied> </ab></div></div>
